file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  description: TBD
  title: QRE API
  version: 0.0.0
servers:
- url: https://api.factset.com
security:
- FactSetApiKey: []
- FactSetOAuth2: []
paths:
  /analytics/quant/qre/v1/calculations:
    post:
      description: This endpoint takes a python script and starts executing it within
        QRE
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/Calculation'
      responses:
        "202":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/CalculationStatus'
          description: Expected response, contains the relative URL in the Location
            header to check the status of the calculation.
          headers:
            Location:
              description: Relative URL to check status of the request.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Relative URL to check status of the request.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "400":
          description: Invalid request body provided
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "500":
          description: Server error. Log the X-DataDirect-Request-Key header to assist
            in troubleshooting.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "503":
          description: Request timeout. Retry the request later
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
      summary: Starts a new script calculation
      tags:
      - Calculations
      x-contentType: application/json
      x-accepts: application/json
  /analytics/quant/qre/v1/calculations/{id}:
    get:
      description: This is the endpoint to check on the progress of a previous calculation
        request.
      parameters:
      - description: From url, provided by location header or response body in the
          calculation start endpoint
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: id
        required: true
        schema:
          description: From url, provided by location header or response body in the
            calculation start endpoint
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/CalculationStatus'
          description: Expected response. Signals that the calculation is finished.
          headers:
            Location:
              description: Relative URL to check status of the request.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Relative URL to check status of the request.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "202":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/CalculationStatus'
          description: Expected response. Signals that the calculation is still in
            progress.
          headers:
            Location:
              description: Relative URL to check status of the request.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Relative URL to check status of the request.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "500":
          description: Server error. Log the X-DataDirect-Request-Key header to assist
            in troubleshooting.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "503":
          description: Request timeout. Retry the request later
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
      summary: Get calculation status by id
      tags:
      - Calculations
      x-accepts: application/json
  /analytics/quant/qre/v1/calculations/{id}/output:
    get:
      description: This endpoint returns the specified output from the calculation.
      parameters:
      - description: From url, provided by location header or response body in the
          calculation start endpoint
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: id
        required: true
        schema:
          description: From url, provided by location header or response body in the
            calculation start endpoint
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            '*':
              schema:
                format: binary
                type: string
          description: Expected response. Signals that the calculation is finished.
            Output from the calculation is returned.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
            Content-Type:
              description: The content type of the output specified in the calculation's
                script.
              explode: false
              schema:
                type: string
              style: simple
        "202":
          description: Expected response. Signals that the calculation is still in
            progress and no output is returned.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "500":
          description: Server error. Log the X-DataDirect-Request-Key header to assist
            in troubleshooting.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "503":
          description: Request timeout. Retry the request later
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
      summary: Get calculation output for a specific calculation
      tags:
      - Calculations
      x-accepts: '*'
  /analytics/quant/qre/v1/calculations/{id}/log:
    get:
      description: This endpoint returns the log from the calculation.
      parameters:
      - description: From url, provided by location header or response body in the
          calculation start endpoint
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: id
        required: true
        schema:
          description: From url, provided by location header or response body in the
            calculation start endpoint
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                format: binary
                type: string
          description: Expected response. Signals that the calculation is finished.
            Log from the calculation is returned.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "202":
          description: Expected response. Signals that the calculation is still in
            progress and no log is returned.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "500":
          description: Server error. Log the X-DataDirect-Request-Key header to assist
            in troubleshooting.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "503":
          description: Request timeout. Retry the request later
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
      summary: Get calculation log for a specific calculation
      tags:
      - Calculations
      x-accepts: text/plain
  /analytics/quant/qre/v1/files/{server}/{file}:
    post:
      description: This endpoint takes a file and uploads it
      parameters:
      - description: The server to upload the file to. Either `interactive` or `batch`.
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: server
        required: true
        schema:
          description: The server to upload the file to. Either `interactive` or `batch`.
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: The file name to upload the file to. Existing directory can be
          specified.
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: file
        required: true
        schema:
          description: The file name to upload the file to. Existing directory can
            be specified.
          type: string
        style: simple
      requestBody:
        content:
          '*':
            schema:
              format: binary
              type: string
      responses:
        "202":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/FileUploadStatus'
          description: Expected response, contains the relative URL in the Location
            header to check the status of the upload.
          headers:
            Location:
              description: Relative URL to check status of the request.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Relative URL to check status of the request.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "500":
          description: Server error. Log the X-DataDirect-Request-Key header to assist
            in troubleshooting.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "503":
          description: Request timeout. Retry the request later
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
      summary: Starts a file upload
      tags:
      - Files
      x-contentType: '*'
      x-accepts: application/json
  /analytics/quant/qre/v1/files/uploads/{id}:
    get:
      description: This is the endpoint to check on the progress of a previous upload
        request.
      parameters:
      - description: From url, provided by location header or response body in the
          upload start endpoint
        explode: false
        in: path
        name: id
        required: true
        schema:
          description: From url, provided by location header or response body in the
            upload start endpoint
          type: string
        style: simple
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/FileUploadStatus'
          description: Expected response. Signals that the upload is finished.
          headers:
            Location:
              description: Relative URL to check status of the request.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Relative URL to check status of the request.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "202":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/FileUploadStatus'
          description: Expected response. Signals that the upload is still in progress.
          headers:
            Location:
              description: Relative URL to check status of the request.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: Relative URL to check status of the request.
                type: string
              style: simple
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "500":
          description: Server error. Log the X-DataDirect-Request-Key header to assist
            in troubleshooting.
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
        "503":
          description: Request timeout. Retry the request later
          headers:
            X-DataDirect-Request-Key:
              description: FactSet's request key header.
              explode: false
              schema:
                description: FactSet's request key header.
                type: string
              style: simple
      summary: Get upload status by id
      tags:
      - Files
      x-accepts: application/json
components:
  schemas:
    Calculation:
      example:
        script: script
      properties:
        script:
          description: The python script that will be executed
          type: string
    CalculationStatus:
      example:
        id: id
        status: pending
      properties:
        id:
          description: The unique ID for this calculation
          type: string
        status:
          enum:
          - pending
          - failed
          - completed
          type: string
    FileUploadStatus:
      example:
        id: id
        status: pending
      properties:
        id:
          description: The unique ID for this upload
          type: string
        status:
          enum:
          - pending
          - failed
          - completed
          type: string
  securitySchemes:
    FactSetOAuth2:
      flows:
        clientCredentials:
          scopes: {}
          tokenUrl: https://auth.factset.com/as/token.oauth2
      type: oauth2
    FactSetApiKey:
      scheme: basic
      type: http
